Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.27,0:01:54.27,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}籠の中は安全で　絶対なのだと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.27,0:01:59.44,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}創造すら忘れたその座に光は当たんないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.48,0:02:01.93,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}希望語る　不満散らす
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.93,0:02:03.82,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}革命の合図
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.95,0:02:08.38,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}誰にも追いつけないところまで突き抜け
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.38,0:02:14.33,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}修羅を越え　いつか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.33,0:02:19.92,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}今に圧倒的な支配が僕の喉を渇かしたとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.92,0:02:24.43,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}奪わせないものは　夢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.56,0:02:27.35,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}燃やせ　全神経の感覚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.40,0:02:32.13,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}誰に届けたいかすらもわからない音に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.13,0:02:37.45,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}意義は宿らない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.33,0:02:37.77,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)\fs55}光を　もっと光を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.92,0:02:40.36,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)\fs55}光を　もっと光を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.47,0:02:42.77,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)\fs55}光を　もっと光を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.77,0:02:46.70,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}その頂きへと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.88,0:02:49.44,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}Have an obsession for victory
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.44,0:02:51.94,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}I'm proud of myself and you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.99,0:02:54.66,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}We must be the change we wish to see...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.27,0:01:54.27,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}在囚籠中是絕對安全的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.27,0:01:59.44,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}但忘卻了創造的地方不會有光明
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.48,0:02:01.93,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}訴說希望 驅散不滿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.93,0:02:03.82,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}革命的信號
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.95,0:02:08.38,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}突破到無人能及的境界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.38,0:02:14.33,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}總有一天要超越修羅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.33,0:02:19.92,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}就算現在壓倒性的支配讓我極度乾渴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.92,0:02:24.43,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}只有夢不會被奪走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.56,0:02:27.35,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}燃燒吧 全部神經的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.40,0:02:32.13,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}不知誰能收到的聲音裏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.13,0:02:37.45,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}不會有意義
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.33,0:02:37.77,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)\fs66}要光明 要更多的光明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.92,0:02:40.36,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)\fs66}要光明 要更多的光明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.47,0:02:42.77,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)\fs66}要光明 要更多的光明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.77,0:02:46.70,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,向着頂點前進
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.88,0:02:49.44,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)\an8}Have an obsession for victory
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.44,0:02:51.94,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)\an8}I'm proud of myself and you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.99,0:02:54.66,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)\an8}We must be the change we wish to see...
